---
title: Caramelized Honey-Garlic Pork Noodles with Snow Peas and Sesame Seeds
description: This dish's sweet and savoury sauce gives ground pork, crisp snow peas and julienned carrots the takeout treatment! Plus, chow mein noodles — traditional Asian egg noodles — are the perfect pairing, for their ability to soak up every last bit of flavour.
